The product is a Next.js dashboard for Meta Ads analysis. It connects to Meta, lets the user choose an account, campaign scope, date range, KPI pack, and comparison mode, then turns the pull into KPI cards, charts, health checks, Verdicts, AI insight briefs, and PDF reports. I checked the current Red Agency Ads repo while updating this case study; the local build is at commit 8acd142, "chore: remove duplicated agent skill instructions".
